metadata.name: YACHTIE
metadata.description: The YACHTIE is a collection of ready-to-play Avatars that brings the #YachtLife into the Metaverse. Each Yachtie Avatar doubles as an entry-pass to the 1st NFT Yachting Community with real-life experiences, metaverse benefits and the 1st Dapps linked to Yachting. Visit www.cyc.community to learn more.
